On VM
-----
Install emacs 26.3

On Host

-> install iterm2
-> regler vitesse frappe preferrence mac
-> creer alias connection vm
-> creer alias open emacs
-> fixer ip vm (tuto https://willwarren.com/2015/04/02/set-static-ip-address-in-vmware-fusion-7/)

conf iterm:
under profile
 - silent bell
 - keys: right option = escape
  -keys key-mapping ^- ignore (for text smaller)
under general profile
 keys -> remap modifiers left command = right option

conf mac keyboard
Mission controle
deactivate f11
deactivate move left a space / move right a space

Shorcuts -> app shortcut
+ ITerm
Close ^(Shift)W
Copy ^(Shift)C
Paste ^(Shift)V
Make Text Smaller ^-
Make Text Bigger ^=
Toggle Full Screen F11
New Tab with Current Profile ^(Shift)T

add ssh-agent
Generate / pub & private keys to host, copy pubic keys to host (ssh-copy-id host)
Add key to agent ssh-add -K
